  "title": "Project Coordinator (Electrical) #77383",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Electrical Engineering and Contracting Services Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Project Coordinator (Electrical)</strong></li><li>Working Location: East – Kaki Bukit</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon to Fri: 8am-5pm, Every Sat:8am-12pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 4000 + AWS</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support the Project Manager in executing awarded projects</li><li>Collaborate with clients, consultants, and main contractors to coordinate project plans and implementation</li><li>Oversee quality checks on ongoing work, providing recommendations for enhanced project management</li><li>Assess and review the work performed by subcontractors</li><li>Compile project reports and ensure drawings are up to date</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. ITE in Electrical/Mechanical or relevant</li><li>Min 1 year of working experience in project management</li><li>Familiar with basic computer skills</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77383 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
